Day 0️⃣4️⃣: Control Structures

Programe to check wether a number is prime or not

print("👋 Hey there! Let's find out what kind of number you've got.\n")

Your_number=int(input("please enter your number:"))

print("=" * 50)
print("🔍 Analyzing your number...")
print("=" * 50)

print("\n📢 Final Result:\n")
if Your_number>1:
    for i in range(2, Your_number):
        if Your_number % i == 0:
            print(f"oops!! {Your_number} is not a prime number.")
            break
    else:
        print(f"hurray!! {Your_number} is a prime number.")
else:
    print("sorry , you entered wrong number!!")
    print(f"{Your_number} is not a possitive number.Please enter number greater than 1")
    
